hopobject.body: How much notice do you have to give? pharmacyvictoria.com reviews Dr. Kiran Patel, local GP and Chair of NHS Bury CCG, said: "Health Matters aims to let you know about our work and how you can get involved and help shape local health services in the future. We are committed to working together with our partners and local people to ensure that local services are responsive, efficient and offer good value for money. Health Matters is just one way that we are reaching out into our local communities to keep people informed and to give them the opportunity to get involved and make a difference."
